        <h1>how to get started with the BBC microbit</h1>
        <p>In my last website I had wrote what the <a target="_blank" href="https://abinnovator.github.io/About%20BBC%20microbit.html">microbit</a> is,In this website I will tell how<br>to code the Microbit.
        <h2>How to code the microbit on computer</h2>
        First GO to the <aá¹ target="blank_ href="https://makecode.microbit.org/">editor</a>.Then you go through the tutoriols or just start your own project by clicking on new<br>project and give it a name.<br>
        After you are done with that connect the microbit to your pc and <a target="_blank" href="https://microbit.org/get-started/user-guide/web-usb/">click on this link for the tutoriul</a>.<br>
        After you are reading all of the things you can start making your new project.Make sure you see my next website to learn more about the microbit</p>
